{{#> base subject="COMPLIANCE ALERT — Sanctions Hit Detected"}}
  {{#*inline "body"}}
    <div class="danger-banner">
      🚨 <strong>IMMEDIATE ACTION REQUIRED — COMPLIANCE ALERT</strong>
    </div>

    <h2>Sanctions Hit Detected</h2>
    <p>A sanctions screening has returned a <strong style="color:#DC2626;">HIT</strong> result for the following client. Immediate compliance review is required.</p>

    <div class="stat-box">
      <div class="label">Client Name</div>
      <div class="value" style="font-size:18px;">{{clientName}}</div>
      <div class="label" style="margin-top:12px;">Client ID</div>
      <div class="value" style="font-size:14px;font-family:monospace;">{{clientId}}</div>
      <div class="label" style="margin-top:12px;">Screened At</div>
      <div class="value" style="font-size:14px;">{{screenedAt}}</div>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Actions taken automatically:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Client KYC status set to <strong>REJECTED</strong></li>
      <li>All pending transactions for this client have been paused</li>
      <li>This alert has been logged in the audit trail</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>Required actions:</strong></p>
    <ol>
      <li>Review the full screening report in the AOP Compliance Dashboard.</li>
      <li>Determine whether this is a true positive or false positive.</li>
      <li>File a Suspicious Activity Report (SAR) if required by applicable law.</li>
      <li>Document your findings and decision in the system.</li>
    </ol>

    <hr class="divider" />
    <p style="color:#888;font-size:13px;">This alert was generated automatically by the ComplyAdvantage sanctions screening engine. Do not forward this email outside your compliance team.</p>
  {{/inline}}
{{/base}}
